{"tid":1695431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"11月10日 請大家出席國殤紀念日 向守衛香港軍人作最高致敬","createTime":"2019-11-05T15:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-08T17:25:37.000Z","uid":119895,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9625376a697980bde3b9446041f8c3162da4b8e5","tid":1695431,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T15:36:33.000Z","msg":"呢一個活動每年由退伍軍人組織舉行, 政府及各大領事館亦會派代表出席, 請大家穿著得體, 尊重場合同儀式, 並佩戴Poppy 以作悼念<br />\n有關活動程序<br />\n和平紀念日 二零一九年十一月十日(星期日)<br />\nREMEMBRANCE DAY - SUNDAY 10 NOVEMBER 2019<br />\n和平紀念碑置獻花圈儀式程序表<br />\nORDER OF CEREMONY AT THE CENOTAPH<br />\n<br />\n1030 集合 ASSEMBLE<br />\n<br />\n1048 儀仗隊進場 PARADE MARCH ON<br />\n參加者就位 ALL PARTICIPANTS IN POSITION<br />\n<br />\n1055 聖職代表就位 CLERGY PARTY IN POSITION<br />\n<br />\n1059 儀 式開始﹝中英語﹞ OPENING ADDRESS (CHINESE &amp; ENGLISH )<br />\n<br />\n1100 號角手吹奏 - &ldquo;安 息 號&rdquo; BUGLER - LAST POST<br />\n<br />\n1101 靜默兩分鐘 TWO MINUTE SILENCE<br />\n<br />\n1103 號角手吹奏 - &ldquo;起 床 號&rdquo; BUGLER - REVEILLE<br />\n<br />\n1105 置獻花圈儀式開始 COMMENCE WREATH LAYING<br />\n獻花儀式進行時蒙警察樂隊 (Music played by Hong Kon g Police Band during wreaths<br />\n奏樂 laying)<br />\n<br />\n1115 聖職代表誦禱文﹝中英語﹞ PRAYERS AND RECITATIONS FOR REMEMBRANCE<br />\nBY CLERGY (CHINESE AND ENGLISH)<br />\n祝福 BLESSING<br />\n<br />\n1125 樂隊奏中國國歌 CHINESE NATIONAL ANTHEM BY THE BAND<br />\n儀仗隊及樂隊離場 GUARDS AND BAND MARCH OFF<br />\n儀式完畢 CEREMONY ENDS<br />\n<br />\n服飾標準 DRESS CODE<br />\n軍人：禮服/軍裝及勳章 Servicemen and women<br />\n&ndash; Ceremonial or Full Service Dress with medals<br />\n平民：西裝、領呔及勳章/女士等同服裝 Civilian<br />\n&ndash; Suit &amp; tie with medals for men and equivalent for ladies<br />\n<br />\n天氣欠佳時安排<br />\n如因天氣欠佳取消儀式，香港退伍軍人聯會主席、英國皇家退伍軍人協會會長及幹事們將會代表<br />\n各獻花人仕置獻全部花圈。如欲親自置獻花圈的人仕或團體代表，請於 10 時 45 分在香港會所前<br />\n的行人通道齊集。 如本港掛起 8 號或以上的風暴 黑色 暴 雨 雷 暴警告信號，則整個儀式將會取消。<br />\n<br />\nINCLEMENT WEATHER ARRANGEMENTS<br />\nIn the event of inclement weather the parade and Remembrance Service would be cancelled. The Chairman of the Ex-Servicemen&rsquo;s Association, the President of the Royal British Legion and committee members will lay all the wreaths. Should wreath-layers wish to attend and lay their wreaths they should assemble at the pedestrian in front of the Hong Kong Club at 1045 hours. If local storm warning signal No. 8 or higher / black rainstorm / thunderstorm is in-forced the whole ceremony will be cancelled."},{"pid":"38767cbd03df2c7373032bbb40ba883059c5c174","tid":1695431,"uid":119895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2f62b46b03f936f0dfdaf996b4f5686314e7ab05","tid":1695431,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3436d9d88ffdfef0fb315ff750f079e64583278c","tid":1695431,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"點解奏支那國歌<br />\n唔係應該係God Save The Queen同Oh Canada <br />\n又或者I vow thee for my country"},{"pid":"3cd81ffb6bffea297bc28b70d5dd69193ff10e04","tid":1695431,"uid":119895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:01:02.000Z","msg":"參與儀式可以順手connect 埋英聯邦各國，感謝佢地70幾年前光復香港既事蹟"},{"pid":"17fcd3466b1e087ed7b3fb566f1c1ad277bb4cfa","tid":1695431,"uid":119895,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3436d9d88ffdfef0fb315ff750f079e64583278c","tid":1695431,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T06:59:42.000Z","msg":"點解奏支那國歌<br />\n唔係應該係God Save The Queen同Oh Canada <br />\n又或者I vow thee for my country"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"呢個係97淪陷後退伍軍人會為左延續個儀式既妥協"},{"pid":"e8f009c6b69ff9341752582d7367e0754351801f","tid":1695431,"uid":119895,"l